TEXT.S: Carlos Alazraqui kawas tay 1962, ryax sa tay 20 nqu tay 7, Carlos Alazraqui, squliq na Bunge'. qnxan nya Carlos Alazraqui htagan beh sa Yonkers, New York. trang laqi musa Concord, California. 1982 1986 kawas mqwas bah California, Sacramento hopa pqwasan biru. Carlos Alazraqui maki sazing kneril laqi, msqun beh Los Angeles.
